<normalizedToken id="28274907B1CB74DD2AA4AFD4900ABC40" originalValue="Liévano">Lievano</normalizedToken>
, 5 Jan. 2017. (HNHM 104157). Paratypes, same data (coll. Grego 1 specimen); type locality, leg. Angyal and 
<normalizedToken id="85E73A3DC38C6B31DAA2A41F6EBB17F5" originalValue="Liévano">Lievano</normalizedToken>
