</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="B1E351F5D5289D0F3BA66DFE7891BEEF" pageId="4" pageNumber="83" type="description">
<paragraph id="282446012736385C4A26C2CEDEEC321F" pageId="4" pageNumber="83">Measurements.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FCAA5358A9A2284BDFC491EC6DEA679E" pageId="4" pageNumber="83">Holotype: H 1.58 mm; W 1.56 mm; WB 1.08 mm; AH 0.90, AW 0.70 (holotype). Figs 11-13. Paratype: H 1.56 mm; W 1.30 mm; WB 1.06 mm; AH 0.84, AW 0.66 (holotype). Figs 14-16.</paragraph>
<caption id="3147AC1C8C9434EAD31263C260D23182" pageId="4" pageNumber="83">
